							That's right!  This Friday the officers of the Crimson Dragons will be holding a meeting at 8pm sharply at a place to be determined (probably Rivervale) with an invasion of paw for all members to follow at 9pm (GMT -05:00).  If you are going to attend the invasion, please post your name and level on the OOC board in the Invade Somewhere thread so we can form groups.That's right!  This Friday the officers of the Crimson Dragons will be holding a meeting at 8pm sharply at a place to be determined (probably Rivervale) with an invasion of paw for all members to follow at 9pm (GMT -05:00).  If you are going to attend the invasion, please post your name and level on the OOC board in the Invade Somewhere thread so we can form groups.
